  "texts": [
    "We independently train each of the two streams until the models converge.",
    "To combine both modalities, we employ a straightforward ensemble method.",
    "Specifically, we retain the outputs from the last fully-connected layers of each modality, before the softmax layer.",
    "These outputs are of size n, where n represents the number of classes.",
    "We then assign weights to each modality based on their accuracy on the validation set, and sum these weighted outputs to form our final predicted score:where F represents the result of each modality, is hyper- parameters to be tuned based on ensemble accuracy on the validation set."
  ],
